Sentencas: Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3 were tested as possible solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) cathode materials.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Their electrical and structural characteristics were studied.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the La(Fe1-xAlx)O-3 system, specific resistivities increase with increasing concentration of Al2O3.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The sintered materials are porous and the average grain diameters decrease with increasing Al2O3 content.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the La1-xCaxFeO3 system, a new single phase, iso-structural with LaFeO3, was observed for x = 0.5.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The room temperature resistivities of La1-xCaxFeOy decrease with increasing values of x, up to x = 0.5.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The resistivity of La0.5Ca0.5FeOy is more than four orders of magnitude lower than the resistivity of LaFeO3.
Titulo: Some characteristics of Al2O3- and CaO-modified LaFeO3-based cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells
